├── docs/                         # Complete SE specification
│   ├── 00-README.md              # Document map and reading order
│   ├── 01-SRS.md                 # IEEE 830/29148 — Software Requirements
│   ├── 02-SAD.md                 # ISO/IEC/IEEE 42010 — Software Architecture
